DISCIPLINARY CASES

2007-1329. In re Schram.

It is ordered by this court, sua sponte, that Deborah C. Schram, Attorney Registration No. 0025554, last known business address in Dayton, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s orders of August 30, 2007, and November 8, 2007, to wit: failure to file an affidavit of compliance on or before November 19, 2007.
